	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002649_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>20 Bedford <choice><abbr>Squ</abbr><expan>Square</expan></choice></placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">8<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> January </p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1858 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Sir </p>
<lb/><p>In reference 
<lb/>to the kind invitation 
<lb/>contained in your 
<lb/>and <persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">rs</hi></hi> Haldane's</persName>
<lb/>note I am sorry 
<lb/>that it will be 
<lb/>out of my power 
<lb/>to come. I am 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002649_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'-->
<lb/>engaged to go 
<lb/>to three kind friends 
<lb/>before my 
<lb/>departure and 
<lb/>have besides 
<lb/>very little time 
<lb/>to spare from 
<lb/>pressing duties<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice>
<lb/>I thank you 
<lb/>most heartily 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002649_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'-->
<lb/>and am with 
<lb/>kind regard to 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">rs</hi></hi> H.</persName></p>
<lb/><p><choice><orig>y</orig><reg>Y</reg></choice>ours truly </p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p><persName>A. Haldane Esq</persName></p>
			
</div>
		</body>
